  <div class="fyre-comment-user">
    <a class="fyre-comment-author"><img src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/867468f6a3870a54936e8d76e90415be/?s=50&amp;d=http://avatars.fyre.co/a/anon/50.jpg" class=
